description:
Shirley Temple's 1933 short "Dora's Dunking Donuts". In this episode Shirley helps Andy Clyde make a radio commercial.

Director: Harry Edwards (as Harry J. Edwards)
Writers: Ernest Pagano (story), Ewart Adamson 
Stars: Andy Clyde, Ethel Sykes, Bud Jamison, Shirley Temple
